milestones.description: Alvin Kallicharran has become the top scorer for WI in ODIs with 378 runs, going past Clive Lloyd's 361
Faoud Bacchus has broken the record for most ducks (2) in ODIs for WI, going past Garry Sobers's 1
Holder has become the top wicket-taker for WI in ODIs with 19 wickets, going past Julien's 18
This is the lowest match aggregate (279) involving teams Australia & West Indies in ODIs
Holder and Shivnarine's 47-run partnership is WI's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 37 between Deryck Murray and Holder
